This Keyword:
-------------
This is a keyword and a reference varaible that refers to current Object. 

1. Used to refer current object variable.
  EX:
   String name = "";
    ThisKeywordDemo(String name){
        this.name = name;
    }

2. Call current class constructor.
   EX:  ThisKeywordDemoConstructor(){
        this.stateName = "Andhra Pradesh";
    }

    ThisKeywordDemoConstructor(String name1, String name2){
        this(name1);
        this.name2 = name2;
    }

    ThisKeywordDemoConstructor(String name){
        this();
        this.name = name;
    }
  
3. pass current object to method.
     public void assignData(PassCurrentObjectAndReturnCurrObj obj){
        obj.name1 = "test";
    }
     public PassCurrentObjectAndReturnCurrObj getCurrInstance(){
