Final Keyword
--------------
1. To restrict modification we use final keyword.

final keyword can be used with:
  -> Variable
  Syntax: final datatype varaiableName = value;
  EX: final int i =10
  
-> Method
  final returntype MethodName(){}
  final void display(){
    sout("Name is test");
  }
  -> We cant Override final method.
   
-> Class
  final class classname{}
  ex: final Class TestFinalDemo{}
  We cant Extend final class.


